1. **`it('inserts a memory_recall part at index 0 on first event')`** — Purpose: asserts the top-of-bubble placement contract. Dispatch a `memory_recall` event, then read `currentPartsRef.current[0]` and assert `type === 'memory_recall'` with `isStreaming: true`.

